@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@coursewareId = cw-course-ai-001
@scriptId = script20260406000000000000
@audioId = audio20260406000000000000

### 发布智课（把 @coursewareId / @scriptId / @audioId 替换成前一步返回值，其中 @coursewareId 来自 parse 完成结果中的 cir.coursewareId）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/lesson/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "coursewareId": "{{coursewareId}}",
  "scriptId": "{{scriptId}}",
  "audioId": "{{audioId}}",
  "publisherId": "teacher-demo",
  "enc": "demo-signature"
}
